{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1678-05_022", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Madrigal de M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[2]", "text": " Petit sur M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[3]", "text": " de Fontenelle]*"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", mai 1678 [tome 5], p. 22-24."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je feray plus, & comme je sçay l’estime que vous avez pour l’Autheur, j’y adjoûteray un Madrigal qui a esté fait à son avantage. Il vous fera voir que vous n’estes pas la seule qui vous étonniez que dans un âge aussi peu avancé que le sien, il pense si juste, & exprime si finement tout ce qu’il pense. M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " Petit, de Rouën, dont je vous ay déja parlé plusieurs fois, en a trouvé une raison assez plausible dans le Madrigal que je vous envoye. Voyez si vous ne serez pas de son sentiment."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Fontenelle, dans ton jeune âge,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "À bien de vieux Rimeurs tu peux faire leçon ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Et quand on lit ton moindre Ouvrage,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui ne t’a jamais veu, te prend pour un Barbon."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Si ta Muse naissante a produit des merveilles,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Et si tes Vers chantez dans le sacré Vallon,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Des plus fin Connoisseurs ont charmé les oreilles,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Pourquoy s’en étonneroit-on ?"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Quand on est Neveu des Corneilles,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "On est Petit-Fils d’Apollon."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}], "attributes": {"rend": "border"}}]}